reputation = Array[String](["Sandora is the largest town in the mountain range situated at the bottom of a waterfall. It is surrounded by small mines, and its streets are filled with the sound of metal work. It’s most famous for its grand quarries. "])
function_one = Array[String](["Quarries and mason's guild. Any constructions performed in this region, or adjacent regions, may have its cost reduced by 25% but take 1 week longer to complete.  "])

