function_one = Array[String](["Strategic location. Armies can directly enter or leave this castle from both Corvinshire and Lydea", "Great Keep. This center has a great keep, which can house 1000 soldiers and any important character. If a city is under siege, the ruling lord and his most loyal followers can hide here until help arrives. "])

